        "text": "Psalm 142:4",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Psalm 143:4",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). Each of the two members of ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Psalm 77:4",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " are protasis and apodosis; concerning this emotional kind of structure of a sentence, vid., Ewald, ֗357, b. ",
